                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-342-defend2366 t18310630-342-punish1807"></join>
               Confined One Year in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SMART - <rs id="t18310630-342-verdict1808" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310630-342-verdict1808" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310630-342-verdict1808" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor.</p>
